{"tid":1444350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不合作運動進化 - 還富於民] lv2 街位免費泊車！！","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T01:36:25.000Z","uid":52817,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a70215fd9c35c6c651ebcebc6b0051c2ab82404c","tid":1444350,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:13:17.000Z","msg":"要對準政權，除左堵塞交通，仲要堵塞其經濟收入。誠然呢類交通收入唔係政府主要收入來源，堵塞收入來源對政府做唔成經濟打擊。但係不合作運動更重要既目的係要受惠市民，令市民既係被動地接受，同時亦有份主動參予，咁可以令市民心態亦都遂步升級，最終目地就係全民接受不合作，罷稅。<br />\n<br />\n我地已經試過好多抗爭方法，政府冇回應，就應遂步升級，lv1係免費隧道，lv2就係免費泊車。唔需要破壞咪錶，直接將個mon噴黑，將閃燈位噴黑就得，有心的話可以係上面貼埋街招，寫幾句口號例如 政府漠視人民，人民漠視咪錶、五大訴求缺一不可、此處免費泊車等。<br />\n<br />\n咪錶唔係不能收費，只係冇野睇按唔到收幾多，亦睇唔到有冇拍卡。市民有心合作應搵可收費既錶，或者唔泊車，直接免費泊係到就被動地主動參予不合作，先從心理上打開佢地參加不合作運動既缺口先。<br />\n<br />\n不過要提醒，免費泊車最終會令更多車冇位泊，而冇位泊車既市民會將矛頭針對發起免費泊車既示威者，抑或造成車位短缺既政府，就難講。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/transport_in_hong_kong/parking/parking_meters/octopus_operated_parking_meters/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ftransport_in_hong_kong%2Fparking%2Fparking_meters%2Foctopus_operated_parking_meters%2Findex.html&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqlznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=a83cacb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/transport_in_hong_kong/parking/parking_meters/octopus_operated_parking_meters/index.html</a> 政府有齊全港泊車錶既位置，請大家backup<br />\n<br />\ntopic係抄<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1437617\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1437617</a>過海隧道免費，俾番個credit佢。"},{"pid":"412ab41dd002b8580b5128aa7322697531ed09df","tid":1444350,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:41:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d18a7b9544b6d27620678989c758b3c225a5d7f","tid":1444350,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:45:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5055af287b57aa16061a1d989c7245dc31aa8018","tid":1444350,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:53:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba1fa7134d931456395562060ff9aac04dea3965","tid":1444350,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5586b3aeb1818029cb952fc96035900a281d37f5","tid":1444350,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602666c6a9c45c6d629d4e4fee0307128dcade93","tid":1444350,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:32:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6cb1e2d8b3711b594596b2d19224551b6498910d","tid":1444350,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:44:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2665608ad6892f3ccd8c3f7c58f08f93375f3bbd","tid":1444350,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9883b854909c12ccb18ff01037be78a268d75e7","tid":1444350,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1f4623f615700b63bd225ecbbd0d1fadd671c75","tid":1444350,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:13:06.000Z","msg":"好似唔岩時候但照推"},{"pid":"53dc5f0860f4ef8fecfdbd7538e495195fd050f0","tid":1444350,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:15:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6916ca46666996beaa42ad9014025ea7785efde2","tid":1444350,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:59:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4ab229eda5f2eb75a6d1ea5c6e62d7c22a4ccf7","tid":1444350,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:03:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77a327e421d245ab0192d01f003e2f2553a33c0f","tid":1444350,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:48:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b578e050f03b445a16931e690c378dbded6